{"title":"Slug Bicycles The Earthling Gravel Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/slug-the-earthling-gravel/","date":1746636919000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike12.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike12.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>First previewed in our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2025-sea-otter-marin-hudski-mondraker-slug-sage-mosaic/#:~:text=Slug%20Bicycles%20Ti%20The%20Earthling%20Gravel%20Bike%20Prototype\" target=\"_blank\">Sea Otter Reportage</a> last month, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/slug-bicycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Slug Bicycles</a> has launched its Bay Area dirt bike, The Earthling. These titanium chassis gravel bikes are made in Taiwan and feature generous tire clearance (700 x 58 mm), refined off-road geometry, a carbon fork, and minimal, sleek branding…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike11.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike11.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike10.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike10.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>The Earthling Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frame: $3,500 (Frameset)</li>\n<li>Complete: $5,600 (GRX 12-speed)</li>\n<li>Premium 3Al-2.5V Titanium</li>\n<li>700 x 58 mm tire clearance</li>\n<li>3D-printed (SLM) Titanium yoke, designed in-house</li>\n<li>Universal Derailleur Hanger.</li>\n<li>Proudly <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/taichung-taiwan-is-a-bicycling-manufacturing-mecca/\" target=\"_blank\">Made in Taiwan</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug-the-earthling-geo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug-the-earthling-geo.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug-the-earthling-geo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug-the-earthling-geo.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p>The Earthling is available in sizes 50 cm through 62 cm with a constant head angle of 71º and 74º seat angle, with 74 mm of bottom bracket drop across all sizes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Slug_Bikes_Earthling_Gravel_bike7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://slugbicycles.com/products/earthling-dirt-bike\" target=\"_blank\">Slug Bicycles</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/slug-the-earthling-gravel/\">Slug Bicycles The Earthling Gravel Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":